{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">AI Simulation with High Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game you observe customized AI nations battle it out to ultimately try to control the world in a massive free-for-all, featuring alliances, revolts, puppet states and all kinds of political twists! <strong>NOTE: This is not a Strategy Game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/God_Mode_50.gif?t=1737138101\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Extensive Map Creator + God Mode Tools</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game comes with premade Maps and Scenarios, but you can unleash your creativity by making your own! <strong><u>Make your maps and borders as complex as you like!</u>\u00a0</strong>Check out\u00a0<strong>hundreds</strong> of High Quality Scenarios on Steam Workshop from historical periods to fantasy worlds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/gifmap.gif?t=1737138101\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Govern world history by controlling nations directly. Carefully edit borders, terrain, nation stats and AI behaviour at any point during the simulation!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">World Building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">View the whole History of your simulations and Statistics to get a better view of past events and nations long gone. With the right settings, world can continue to change for thousands of years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/History.gif?t=1737138101\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you are interested in <strong>History, Geography, Map Painting</strong> or watching chaos unfold, Ages of Conflict has you covered!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginner Map Maker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/de4eeb3dfc51b833ad4edede94c34442f3e6fa38.jpg"},{"name":"Geopolitical Architect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/568120efa04cb66b62ba39414a2d158638ea96fa.jpg"},{"name":"Member of the Community","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/08b712e8b62e8df35764b97067e2bcbb48452ac2.jpg"},{"name":"Making History","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/acbe79bddc785ebe893aa83fce0df0d1cb0576df.jpg"},{"name":"Eternal Observer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/23e518779a40f652ccc5f38c1de9ee8bf7fa180c.jpg"},{"name":"God Complex","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/3f812227d048699c5c2c8c4faece61b763ef03b8.jpg"},{"name":"Last One Standing","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/7692022f8927f868c67298d01b033dd52625260d.jpg"},{"name":"From Rags to Riches","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/5f4bf63b6c50a587a73479b6d24db564d6bbbb26.jpg"},{"name":"Power to the People","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/e2b704e3d713beca26227f737b399980fdc32270.jpg"},{"name":"Unbreakable Spirit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2186320/fa2bacafbf602573757bb50ae5ab4830c70dedea.jpg"}],"total":11},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737138101","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737138101","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st