/apps/2186320/extras/gifmap.gif?t=1737138101\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Govern world history by controlling nations directly. Carefully edit borders, terrain, nation stats and AI behaviour at any point during the simulation!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">World Building</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">View the whole History of your simulations and Statistics to get a better view of past events and nations long gone. With the right settings, world can continue to change for thousands of years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/extras/History.gif?t=1737138101\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you are interested in <strong>History, Geography, Map Painting</strong> or watching chaos unfold, Ages of Conflict has you covered!</p>","developers":["JoySpark Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2186320/header_alt_assets_3.jpg?t=1737138101","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> 64-bit system<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Quad Core 1.60 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 1 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 150 MB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> 64-bit system<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Apple Silicon or Intel, 1.60 GHz<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 1 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 170 MB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong>